_:N9b9b21cbd97748ccbda2f1eaa39ffb14 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Martin Turner is a senior executive with 18 years extensive experience operating at board level in a variety of roles with complex FTSE 100 organisations in the UK and internationally. He has an excellent track record of successfully leading transformational business and organisational change.</p>\n\n<p>Martin’s current role is Group Business Risk Director for Lloyds Banking Group. This includes accountability for significant Group wide projects and the Risk Chief Operating Office.</p>\n\n<p>His previous roles in Lloyds and Barclays covered integration, compliance and operational risk, IT and operations, servicing and transformation, strategy and planning and change. He has previous experience in a number of project management roles and frontline retail and commercial roles in the UK and Africa.</p>\n" .
